# Webconverger for Raspberry PI 2 port

A curated Archlinux Arm (alarm) rootfs <https://github.com/webconverger/rpi2>
using webkit2gtk based surf2 and a new [Websocket based
updater](https://github.com/Webconverger/wsc) allowing for instant updates to
the configuration.

Currently this port is designed for <abbr title="Digital Out of
Home">DOOH</abbr> applications. It can be used as a kiosk, though it will not
have a "chrome", i.e. [[user interface options|kiosk]],
